{"tid":2267750,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"螞蟻港股暗盤成交 較招股價升35-50%","createTime":"2020-11-02T09:49:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T00:32:20.000Z","uid":152630,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b882b18c69955e1ee69c306540316a07316f9897","tid":2267750,"uid":152630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:49:19.000Z","msg":"【螞蟻港股錄得3宗暗盤成交 較招股價升35-50%】螞蟻集團將於本周四掛牌，其散戶的暗盤交易場要在周三收市后才進行，但機構投資者已率先交易買賣。機構投資者之間就螞蟻的暗盤交易今日錄得3宗成交，成交價分別為108港元、115港元及120港元，較招股價80港元，升35%、43.75%及50%。（新浪財經）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb5decf5511d78f53de5855ce91f6068b435b1a","tid":2267750,"uid":260300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:50:33.000Z","msg":"已經宣佈中籤?"},{"pid":"4c457b67971dbb279eb0a38a851e49aa7d43333a","tid":2267750,"uid":373220,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6fb5decf5511d78f53de5855ce91f6068b435b1a","tid":2267750,"uid":260300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:50:33.000Z","msg":"已經宣佈中籤?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:51:07.000Z","msg":"我都未知中唔中"},{"pid":"7b4a2a53d99f397b032bad4c00e7b0e7d75ba902","tid":2267750,"uid":152630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:53:40.000Z","msg":"阿爺派錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f145ca0b765404c19231f056f1b04f58b3214e1","tid":2267750,"uid":7444,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6fb5decf5511d78f53de5855ce91f6068b435b1a","tid":2267750,"uid":260300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:50:33.000Z","msg":"已經宣佈中籤?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:54:15.000Z","msg":"正常係星期三先知"},{"pid":"d3c3c5a